{"tid":1836831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（香港毒蛇陣吖嗱）中国學者：病毒來源可能是蛇","createTime":"2020-01-23T10:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T15:15:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67e9f1b24408fc855d5cc83bc6f8dff0545af392","tid":1836831,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"中國武漢爆發的新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV）肺炎疫情持續升溫，中國官方22日證實，新病毒來自當地華南海鮮市場出售的野生動物，最新研究進一步指出，病毒來源除了先前提過的蝙蝠，可能還有蛇。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，中國科學院主辦的學術期刊《中國科學：生命科學》（Science China Life Sciences）21日刊登的一篇論文指出，研究發現，武漢出現的新型冠狀病毒與蝙蝠攜帶的病毒密切相關。中國研究人員在論文中指出，病毒從蝙蝠傳到人類，可能存有中間宿主，但並未推測可能是哪種動物。<br />\n<br />\n研究發現，病毒從蝠蝙傳染到人體之前，可能已突變。研究人員再次進行新病毒基因序列的更詳細生物資訊分析，發現這種新病毒可能來自蛇。該論文稱，RSCU分析使用了雨傘節和中華眼鏡蛇。這是華南地區及東南亞常見的毒蛇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3048691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3048691&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=a6e0b101\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3048691&h=3d0ff826\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3048691</a>"},{"pid":"865544ee87be834048d985f3c723851ded2a8e7b","tid":1836831,"uid":265708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會由屎傳染？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19cSo7T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19cSo7T.jpg&h=e6cbfcda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36d80ac852aac98b66c4e4cd0ddfdc286060cc45","tid":1836831,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3d8ecb61390aefbbc9dfc09922255816740b58","tid":1836831,"uid":308964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:15:29.000Z","msg":"有可靠消息指病毒係來自林鄭個大臭閪窿"}]}